{"id": "https://wineindustryadvisor.com/2026/06/10/untitled-8/", "url": "https://wineindustryadvisor.com/2026/06/10/untitled-8/", "title": "A Look Inside THE ROOT: Two Varieties Worth Knowing", "summary": "<img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"292\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1781022497336_6739d7d0.png\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"638\" /><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"292\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1781022497336_6739d7d0.png\" width=\"638\" /></p>In this year's edition of THE ROOT, we spotlight two unique Loire Valley grapes: Pineau d'Aunis and Grolleau Noir. Pineau d'Aunis is celebrated for its distinctive peppery spice and vibrant red fruit character, while Grolleau Noir offers bright acidity, fresh berry flavors, and remarkable versatility across sparkling, rosé, and still wines.", "content": "<img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"292\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1781022497336_6739d7d0.png\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"638\" /><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"292\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1781022497336_6739d7d0.png\" width=\"638\" /></p>In this year's edition of THE ROOT, we spotlight two unique Loire Valley grapes: Pineau d'Aunis and Grolleau Noir. Pineau d'Aunis is celebrated for its distinctive peppery spice and vibrant red fruit character, while Grolleau Noir offers bright acidity, fresh berry flavors, and remarkable versatility across sparkling, rosé, and still wines.", "published_at": "2026-06-10 23:07:08+00:00", "source_name": "Wine Industry Advisor", "source_type": "media", "language": "en", "content_type": "market_report", "country": "US", "continent": "NEW_WORLD", "region": "Americas/North/USA", "producer_role": "trade_media", "trust_tier": "T3_professional", "info_purpose": ["P2_market_analysis"], "collection_tier": "C1_rss"}
