{"id": "https://wineindustryadvisor.com/2026/06/10/untitled-4/", "url": "https://wineindustryadvisor.com/2026/06/10/untitled-4/", "title": "Tariff Refund Opportunity for Wineries", "summary": "<img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"258\" src=\"https://win-advisor-media-library.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/18014545/Brotemarkle-Davis-Co.jpg\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"320\" /><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"258\" src=\"https://win-advisor-media-library.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/18014545/Brotemarkle-Davis-Co.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></p>If you purchased these items through a U.S. distributor, the importer of record would typically be the distributor. This change in policy creates a potential opportunity for wineries that imported certain goods directly during the affected period.", "content": "<img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"258\" src=\"https://win-advisor-media-library.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/18014545/Brotemarkle-Davis-Co.jpg\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"320\" /><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"258\" src=\"https://win-advisor-media-library.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/18014545/Brotemarkle-Davis-Co.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></p>If you purchased these items through a U.S. distributor, the importer of record would typically be the distributor. This change in policy creates a potential opportunity for wineries that imported certain goods directly during the affected period.", "published_at": "2026-06-10 23:05:13+00:00", "source_name": "Wine Industry Advisor", "source_type": "media", "language": "en", "content_type": "market_report", "country": "US", "continent": "NEW_WORLD", "region": "Americas/Nort