{"id": "https://wineindustryadvisor.com/2026/06/10/untitled-6/", "url": "https://wineindustryadvisor.com/2026/06/10/untitled-6/", "title": "Saving Pennies or Saving Dollars?", "summary": "<img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"455\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1780698043569_0032818a.jpg\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"640\" /><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"829\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1780698043569_0032818a.jpg\" width=\"1167\" /></p>Contact your ATPGroup representative or call (707) 836-6840 to discuss practical opportunities for Enology cost optimization. This article is Part 2 of a four-part series exploring a broader approach to winery cost optimization, including evaluating every cost-savings opportunity across winery operations.", "content": "<img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"455\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1780698043569_0032818a.jpg\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"640\" /><p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"829\" src=\"https://wineindustryadvisor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/1780698043569_0032818a.jpg\" width=\"1167\" /></p>Contact your ATPGroup representative or call (707) 836-6840 to discuss practical opportunities for Enology cost optimization. This article is Part 2 of a four-part series exploring a broader approach to winery cost optimization, including evaluating every cost-savings opportunity across winery operations.", "published_at": "2026-06-10 23:06:14+00:00", "source_name": "Wine Industry Advisor", "source_type": "media", "language": "en", "content_type": "market_report", "country": "US", "continent": "NEW_WORLD", "region": "Americas/North/USA", "producer_role": "tra